<p align="center"><br>
<font><font> </font></font></p>
<p><span style="" lang="FR-CA">1939: Creation of the
important dramatic series "Le th&eacute;&acirc;tre de chez-nous" at
CKAC, directed
by Henri Letondal. <o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p>1940: On June 18, General Charles De Gaulle sends out a call to the
French
over the BBC in London, to organize resistance to the German invader. <span
 style="" lang="FR-CA"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;" align="center"><br>
<span style="font-weight: bold;">Advertisement for CJAD
(19 K)</span></p>
